  <section class="paragraph paragraph--type--intro-copy paragraph--view-mode--default wwf-page-section">
          <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="field-intro-copy wwf-text--first-paragraph-bold wwf-text--lg-sm wwf-text--xl-lg">
      <p><em><strong>Will you join the Guardians and protect this vital biome?</strong></em></p><p>WWF Guardians are a group of loyal and generous supporters who each year help fund a specific and vital area of work with a minimum donation of £1,000.</p><p>Over the years, WWF Guardians have been instrumental in helping protect disappearing habitats, fragile ecosystems and endangered species.</p><p>Join the Guardians today and you’ll play a crucial role in tackling some of the biggest challenges we face. You’ll receive exclusive updates on how the work you support is progressing and invites to special events and talks around the country.&nbsp;</p>
