<blockquote>
<p class="text-align-center Paragraph SCXW64224359 BCX0"><span class="TextRun SCXW35894177 BCX0 NormalTextRun" lang="EN-GB"><strong>“Maybe when we draw the last river, maybe when we cut the last tree, maybe then we will realise the importance of nature. The importance of the forest.”</strong></span></p>
